<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

    <PropertyGroup>
        <TargetFrameworks>netstandard2.0;net451;net461</TargetFrameworks>
        <PackageVersion>3.0.0</PackageVersion>
        <Version>3.0.0</Version>
        <Title>LochNessBuilder</Title>
        <AssemblyTitle>LochNessBuilder</AssemblyTitle>
        <Product>LochNessBuilder</Product>
        <PackageTags>builder tests testObjects Loch Ness Builder LochNess LochNessBuilder NessBuilder MonsterBuilder</PackageTags>
        <Authors>JonArtus Brondahl dhedey benbelow Edisach olevett</Authors>
        <Company>Softwire</Company>
        <Copyright>Copyright © 2015</Copyright>
        <PackageLicenseUrl>http://opensource.org/licenses/MIT</PackageLicenseUrl>
        <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/Softwire/LochNessBuilder</RepositoryUrl>
        <GeneratePackageOnBuild>true</GeneratePackageOnBuild>
        <PackageOutputPath>../nuget</PackageOutputPath>
        <DocumentationFile>bin\$(Configuration)\$(TargetFramework)\$(AssemblyName).xml</DocumentationFile>
        <Description>A C# Builder library to automate and commonise creation of objects for tests.
v3.0.0 renames large portions of the API for greater clarity and discoverability</Description>
        <PackageReleaseNotes>Version 3.0.0
* Lots of method/type names have changed between v2.0 and v3.0, but there's very little _functionality_ change, so it should be very easy to migrate.
  * The `[Builder]` attribute renamed to `[BuilderFactory]`.
  * `With(m =&gt; m.SubObject)` intended to auto-find any existing builders, is now `WithBuilt(m =&gt; m.SubObject)`.
  * `With(m =&gt; m.SingleString, "a", "b", "c" )` intended to loop over values, is now `WithOneOf(m =&gt; m.SingleString, "a", "b", "c" )`.
  * `WithCollection(...)` is now `WithEnumerable(...)`.
  * The implicit cast from `Builder&lt;T&gt;` to `T` has been removed. Replace it with calling `.Build()` on the builder.</PackageReleaseNotes>
    </PropertyGroup>
</Project>
